Privacy Policy for Sky Q Remote Control App
Introduction
Welcome to the Sky Q Remote Control app (the "App"), developed by MSDC Technologies Ltd ("we," "us," or "our"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it through our compliance with this policy. This policy explains how we handle your data when you use our App.
1. Data Collection and Usage
We do not collect, store, or process any personal data through the App. This means that:
We do not collect any information from you, such as name, email address, or location. We do not track any activity or interaction within the App. No usage data or personally identifiable information (PII) is gathered or stored by us. 2. Third-Party Advertisements
The App displays advertisements from third-party advertising partners. These third-party providers may collect data to serve you more relevant ads. This data collection is subject to each provider's privacy policy and may include:
Device identifiers, such as IP address and device model. App usage data, such as frequency of app usage and interaction with ads. We do not have access to or control over the data collected by these third-party advertisers. For more information, we encourage you to review the privacy policies of the respective advertising networks displayed within the App.
3. Links to External Sites
The App may contain links to external websites. Please note that we do not control these sites, and they are not governed by this Privacy Policy. We recommend that you review the privacy policy of each site you visit.
4. Security
Although we do not collect data directly, we are committed to maintaining a secure environment for our users. We take measures to ensure that third-party advertisements meet industry security standards. However, we cannot guarantee complete security of your data when interacting with third-party services.
5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:
MSDC Technologies Ltd
Thank you for using the Sky Q Remote Control app. Your trust and privacy are important to us.